selftests/bpf: Adjust data size to have ETH_HLEN

jira LE-4076
cve CVE-2025-21867
Rebuild_History Non-Buildable kernel-6.12.0-55.29.1.el10_0
commit-author Shigeru Yoshida <syoshida@redhat.com>
